*Trebala* je da se udvostruči radna snaga. (It was necessary to double the workforce.)

*Trebalo* bi da se dogovore novi uslovi. (It would be necessary to agree on new terms.)

Svi smo *trebali* da se uključimo u projekat. (We all were supposed to take part in the project.)

Ona je *trebala* da obezbedi novi materijal. (She was supposed to provide new material.)

*Trebalo* bi da se poveća budžet za projekat. (It would be necessary to increase the budget for the project.)